						<div class="postbody">Some very interesting information, Eugene!
<br />
<br />But I seriously doubt that those chips are made by the "real" Hitachi and Toshiba.  They are generically-named clones coming from the usual places, China or Taiwan.
<br />
<br />The first Dendy system picture that you linked to is the same design as the Micro Genius IQ-501.  Is this the original design of the Dendy?
<br />
<br />Finally, does the word "Dendy" have any sort of meaning?</div>

					
